# MQTT Communication Rules (Tc3_IotBase)

## 1. Required Library

```xml
<PlaceholderReference Include="Tc3_IotBase">
  <DefaultResolution>Tc3_IotBase, * (Beckhoff Automation GmbH)</DefaultResolution>
